{"tid":1068821,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人根本就係賤","createTime":"2019-03-19T13:28:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-19T13:42:55.000Z","uid":194135,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ff87efcf6a94d19289e8adde36b16b70e8cfcab7","tid":1068821,"uid":194135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T13:28:09.000Z","msg":"利申：唔係要去踩低香港人吹噓大陸幾好，大家一齊死返去大灣區啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔該唔好再用乜野好客之市黎打飛機 黎麻醉自己一定要用普通話黎應付大陸人<br />\n你地返大陸好&hellip;&hellip;去大陸旅行好&hellip;&hellip;人地會唔會同你講廣東話應付你？除非你返廣州人地係用廣東話既地方<br />\n然後你一定會講咁外國人黎香港你唔屌佢地？係呀～我係歧視呀，唔鍾意呀？返大灣區囉<br />\n然後一定有人企出黎屌而家香港係國際城市，你唔用普通話你咪唔夠國際，食唔到大陸市場囉<br />\n食？人地整個大灣區出黎當你係生金蛋既雞咋懵撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b7d3b77c7326d3d0a858f93d03d3630e8597724","tid":1068821,"uid":226231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T13:34:54.000Z","msg":"無返過大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99f8d82b55a6639257298b2072c39ab10f0e425e","tid":1068821,"uid":77220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T13:35:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BmCeNeW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBmCeNeW.gif&h=7a7eeab1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d0e8e131ca59ba880032d3e46683e25c5dced6f8","tid":1068821,"uid":194135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b7d3b77c7326d3d0a858f93d03d3630e8597724","tid":1068821,"uid":226231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T13:34:54.000Z","msg":"無返過大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T13:42:55.000Z","msg":"唔洗返大陸都感受到果種氣氛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}